  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras/ee4742f8bdb4f017056fc5e2f61a2ab6.avif?t=1738201484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras_big/ee4742f8bdb4f017056fc5e2f61a2ab6.avif?t=1738201484 width=800 height=242 /></span><strong><i>\"My friend Mango\"</i></strong> is a 3D platform game where the player controls Mango, a little dog that comes from the afterlife in search of his best friend. It will have to overcome different challanges, break through between multiple enemies and choose the right path to meet his friend again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras/290790975417b0bb7e8b70b41ac0111a.avif?t=1738201484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras_big/290790975417b0bb7e8b70b41ac0111a.avif?t=1738201484 width=800 height=242 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras/ee4742f8bdb4f017056fc5e2f61a2ab6.avif?t=1738201484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras_big/ee4742f8bdb4f017056fc5e2f61a2ab6.avif?t=1738201484 width=800 height=242 /></span><strong><i>\"My friend Mango\"</i></strong> is a 3D platform game where the player controls Mango, a little dog that comes from the afterlife in search of his best friend. It will have to overcome different challanges, break through between multiple enemies and choose the right path to meet his friend again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras/290790975417b0bb7e8b70b41ac0111a.avif?t=1738201484\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267370/extras_big/290790975417b0bb7e8b70b41ac0111a.avif?t=1738201484 width=800 height=242 /></span></p>",
